    • getNullable

      @Nullable <T> T getNullable(Ext<T> ext)
      Get the value associated with ext in this container, or null if not present.

      If an ext was attached with attachExt(Ext, Object), it should be returned, unless it was later removed with a call to removeExt(Ext).

      Type Parameters:
      T - The type of the ext.
      Parameters:
      ext - The ext.
      Returns:
